    "description": "K Raheja Corp has an exciting opening for a Sales Manager at our Ranchi office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout K Raheja Corp:\nK Raheja Corp is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Title Search\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ranchi, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with K Raheja Corp!",
